     **Race[0m[2m conditions:**[0m[2m
     
     1. **O[0m[2mverselling (inventory[0m[2m goes negative):**[0m[2m
        - Multiple concurrent[0m[2m orders[0m[2m can pass `[0m[2mcheck_stock()`[0m[2m simultaneously when[0m[2m stock is,[0m[2m say, 1[0m[2m
        - Both[0m[2m proceed[0m[2m to charge and[0m[2m decrement[0m[2m
