     **The[0m[2m fix:**
     The[0m[2m core[0m[2m issue is that `[0m[2mcheck_stock()`[0m[2m and `decrement[0m[2m()` are separate[0m[2m operations with[0m[2m a gap[0m[2m between[0m[2m them. We[0m[2m need to make the[0m[2m reservation atomic.[0m[2m
     
     The solution is to[0m[2m add a `reserve[0m[2m()` method to[0m[2m Inventory that atom[0m[2mically checks and decre[0m[2mments stock in[0m[2m one operation. Then[0m[2m the[0m[2m checkout flow becomes:[0m[2m
     1. Reserve inventory[0m[2m (atomic check +[0m[2m decrement)
     2.[0m[2m Charge payment
